      • updateBookingList

        public void updateBookingList​(java.lang.String type)
        Method for updating the list of bookings shown. It clears the current list, and then gets all Bookings from the model that fit the type given as argument and adds them.
        Parameters:
        type - The type of bookings to get for the table, can be either booked or in progress.
